<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Robe of the Lost Circle Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Brother Qwinn in S. Karana to receive the quest.  He asks for the code of whistling fist.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Solusek B and kill Targin the Rock to retrieve this item.  Targin is a very rare spawn in the Throne Room.<BR>
<BR>
3) Take the code of the whisling fist and a purple silent fist headband to Brother Qwinn in S. Karana.  He will give you a needle.<BR>
<BR>
4) Head to the Rathe Mountains and talk to Brother Zephyl.  He asks for the Idol of Zan Fi.  <BR>
<BR>
5) Head to Lower Guk and visit the Mino Elders room.  A rare spawn in this room, Brother Raster, will drop the Idol.<BR>
<BR>
6) Give the Idol and a red sash to Brother Zephyl to receive a pattern.<BR>
<BR>
7) Combine the needle, the pattern, a swatch of shadow silk, and a Scroll of Jonathan's Whistling Warsong to receive the Robe of the Lost Circle.  The Scroll can be purchased in Bard Guilds.</div>
<BR>
