<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Apparently the Idol is very hard to get I have heard of many people camping for 100+ hours with no luck. However I was lucky and found raster the second time I looked. <BR>
At the moment you can fail on the combine when you put all the stuff in your sewing kit, I would advise that you wait for the next patch as I heard they are going to remove the skill check on the combine.<BR>
This robe is the 1st part of the quest for the "robe of the whistling fist". The ROTWF has 15ac and an effect of the level 7 bard haste song which stackes with other haste items.</font></td></tr></table>
